 Figma is telling us not to callÂ showUIÂ directly in the function bodyâ€¦ So, where should we put it? The answer to that is one new hook and one new function:Â useEffectÂ andÂ waitForTask. You might already have familiarity withÂ useEffectÂ if youâ€™re a React developer, but weâ€™re gonna use it here to fetch data from the server when the widget component mounts.



