 CodePen Embed Fallback



 Weâ€™re not changing a thing as far as simulating the cube the same way we did before, other than changing the loaderâ€™s height and aspect ratio. The animation weâ€™re making relies on a surprisingly easy technique where we update the width of the left side while the right side fills the remaining space, thanks to flex-grow: 1.



